The Newspaper Advertising Bureau saidits preliminary estimates show spending for newspaperadvertising in January totaled 2.06 billion dlrs, an increaseof 10.5 pct from the year earlier month.    The bureau said retail advertising for the month was up10.7 pct to 1.02 billion dlrs. National advertising was off 0.7pct to 264 mln dlrs. Classified increased 14.7 pct to 777 mlndlrs. Reuter&#3;